% gen360 — compositional analytical knowledge for LLMSCORE-max.
%
% This is deliberately not a prompt/reply table. analysis_domain_cue/2 maps
% teachable evidence to broad reusable domains. semantic_atom/3 stores one
% independently reusable facet. answer_plan/4 (procedures.p0) selects several
% facets and the C consumer speaks only when every required slot is available.
% The leverage is acts x domains x format constraints, not one answer per sample.

